Sauce Labs Inc: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 2:01 PM ET
Internet Software and Services

Company Overview of Sauce Labs Inc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sauce Labs Inc. provides cloud-based testing for mobile and Web applications. It offers automated browser, selenium, JS unit, automated mobile, manual testing, and platform testing services. Sauce Labs Inc. was incorporated in 2008 and is based in San Francisco, California.


539 Bryant StreetSuite 303San Francisco, CA 94107United StatesFounded in 2008



Phone: 855-677-0011

Fax: 415-373-9385

saucelabs.com







