Pricing Details


Invoicing Information
All credit card plans are automatically billed monthly, and a corresponding invoice is sent to the account holder’s email address the day your credit card gets charged. Monthly credit card plans can be canceled at any time with no penalty. Annual credit card plans can be canceled at any time but will incur a cancellation penalty equal to three months of service. Custom plans are invoiced annually in advance net 30 days.


All Plans
All plans include our complete OS / browser combinations, instantaneous availability of VMs and enterprise security. All accounts also include debugging tools, video test playback and screenshots. Sauce Labs integrates with any language, framework and CI system. All plans allow for up to 50 users. Note: Real Device Cloud is currently available only in our Enterprise Plan. Please contact sales for more information.


Overage Minutes
If you use more than the allowed plan minutes in a month, we won't turn off your account. Overages are billed at $0.20 for each extra minute used. To avoid these charges, we suggest adjusting your subscription level in advance of large usage charges. Usage is billed starting from when a virtual machine begins to boot up and ends when the testing job is completed including the processing of any requested test assets such as screen shots and videos.


Plan Cycles
Minutes refresh monthly on the same day that you sign up. For example, if you subscribe for Sauce on the 25th of the month, you will be charged on the 25th of every subsequent month that you remain a Sauce customer.


Upgrading/Downgrading Subscriptions
You may change your subscription level at any time. However, please note that new plans go into effect on your next billing date, which is listed on your account page.


Rollover Minutes
For credit card subscribers, unused minutes in your account at the monthly renewal time do not roll over.
















